    "sections": {
        "description": "<p><a href=\"https://fondy.io/gb/plugins/restrict-content-pro/?utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_medium=cms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">This Restrict Content Pro payment plugin</a> adds Fondy as payment gateway to Restrict Content Pro. Fondy can accept VISA and MasterCard securely, quickly and easily on your store in minutes. Recurring payments, simple, straightforward pricing, top notch fraud intelligence, and 24/7 support.</p>\n<h3>Start with Fondy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://portal.fondy.eu/mportal/#/account/registration?utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_medium=cms\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Create Free Fondy Account</a></p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Customize your checkout window (<a href=\"http://jsfiddle.net/8h65h91t/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Some styles</a>)</li>\n<li>Easy configuration &#8211; only Merchant ID and Secret Key!</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Allowed currencies</h3>\n<p>With us your customers can make purchases in many currencies. Fondy support  EUR, USD, GBP, UAH and some other.</p>\n<h3>Fondy pricing</h3>\n<p>Clear pricing with no hidden costs <a href=\"https://fondy.io/gb/pricing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">More info</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Make sure you have the latest version of the Restrict Content Pro plug-in</li>\n<li>Unzip this plugin in the directory <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code></li>\n<li>Activate the plug-in in the menu &#8220;Plugins&#8221;<br />\nConfiguration:</li>\n<li>Go to &#8220;Restrict &gt; Settings &gt; Payments&#8221; and find Fondy and activate</li>\n<li>In the &#8220;Fondy RCP payment&#8221; tab, enter the Fondy Secret Key and Fondy MID.</li>\n<li>Save settings.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>Some answers you can find here <a href=\"https://fondy.io/en/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></p>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release</li>\n</ul>\n"
